channel.title: Looking For A Coder For My New Server
channel.description:
Hi I am pennstat3 , owner of iholyscape i have just made my server and i am looking for a coder. i will give admin to whoever i pick to be my coder. plus i will give +rep plz pm me or post here . i have made a hamachi and it is iholyscape1 through iholyscape3 ( theres iholyscape1 , iholyscape2 , and iholyscape3 ) password on all servers is iholy. thank u every1
remember free admin and +rep but only if ur a good coder dont come in and not kno half the stuff i ask u and expect me to pick u...also..BE PATIENT WITH ME
